{"id": "rig1719386303130", "title": "clear", "breadcrumbs": ["Uniface Reference", "ProcScript Reference", "ProcScript: Statements", "clear"], "url": "https://docs.rocketsoftware.com/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rig1719386303130.html", "html": "<html><body><header class=\"zDocsTopicPageHead\"><h1 class=\"css-g931ng\">clear</h1><div class=\"zDocsTopicActions\" role=\"list\"><div class=\"zDocsBundlePagination\" data-testid=\"next-prev-container\" role=\"listitem\"><div class=\"zDocsPrevTopicButton zDocsPrevTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Previous: catch  \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Previous: catch  \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lhc1665702761265.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-prev\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-prev\"></use></svg></a></span></div><div class=\"zDocsNextTopicButton zDocsNextTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Next: close  \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Next: close  \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ifn1665702634315.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></a></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsMyDocsMenu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Add to My Topics\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Add to My Topics\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" id=\"addToMyDocsDropdownTrigger\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg>Add to My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/rig1719386303130.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/rig1719386303130.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/rig1719386303130.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_7423320\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_7423320\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 23, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104rig1719386303130.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rig1719386303130.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rig1719386303130.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"fas1665702598144\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"fas1665702598144__clear_211452\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Clear data from the component or entity.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"fas1665702598144__topic_d70049e1_d70050e1_d70051e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" id=\"fas1665702598144__codeblock_whf_1wz_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">clear{/e  Entity}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fas1665702598144__topic_d45932e1_d45933e1_d45934e1_d45935e1_d45936e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d884696e65\">\n                       \n Qualifiers\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6164e1_d6165e1_d6166e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Qualifiers</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6164e1_d6165e1_d6166e1__entry__1\">\n Qualifier\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6164e1_d6165e1_d6166e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6164e1_d6165e1_d6166e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/e</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6164e1_d6165e1_d6166e1__entry__2\"> Clears data from the specified entity, rather\n                        than the component. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fas1665702598144__topic_d45937e1_d45938e1_d45939e1_d45940e1_d45941e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d884696e111\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6167e1_d6168e1_d6169e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6167e1_d6168e1_d6169e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6167e1_d6168e1_d6169e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6167e1_d6168e1_d6169e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6167e1_d6168e1_d6169e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6167e1_d6168e1_d6169e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6167e1_d6168e1_d6169e1__entry__3\">\n Entity to be cleared. Can be a string, or a field, variable, function, or parameter that evaluates to a string containing the entity name.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fas1665702598144__topic_d45942e1_d45943e1_d45944e1_d45945e1_d45946e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d884696e165\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6170e1_d6171e1_d6172e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span></span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6170e1_d6171e1_d6172e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6170e1_d6171e1_d6172e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6170e1_d6171e1_d6172e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6170e1_d6171e1_d6172e1__entry__2\">\n Data was successfully cleared, or no entities are painted on the component.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6170e1_d6171e1_d6172e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-3</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6170e1_d6171e1_d6172e1__entry__2\">\n Exceptional I/O error (hardware or software).\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6170e1_d6171e1_d6172e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-16</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6170e1_d6171e1_d6172e1__entry__2\">\n Network error: unknown.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6173e1_d6174e1_d6175e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 4. </span><span class=\"title\">Values commonly returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> following\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">clear</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6173e1_d6174e1_d6175e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6173e1_d6174e1_d6175e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Error constant\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6173e1_d6174e1_d6175e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6173e1_d6174e1_d6175e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-2</code> through  <code class=\"ph codeph\">-12</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6173e1_d6174e1_d6175e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UIOSERR_*&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6173e1_d6174e1_d6175e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Errors during database I/O.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6173e1_d6174e1_d6175e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-16</code> through  <code class=\"ph codeph\">-30</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6173e1_d6174e1_d6175e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UNETERR_*&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6173e1_d6174e1_d6175e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Errors during network I/O.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6173e1_d6174e1_d6175e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1102</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6173e1_d6174e1_d6175e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_ENTITY&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fas1665702598144__table_d6173e1_d6174e1_d6175e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n The entity name provided is not a valid name or the entity is not painted on the component.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fas1665702598144__topic_d45947e1_d45948e1_d45949e1_d45950e1_d45951e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d884696e356\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fas1665702598144__p_d70067e1_d70068e1_d70069e1\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fas1665702598144__p_d70070e1_d70071e1_d70072e1\">Not allowed in the <code class=\"ph codeph\">getFocus</code> and\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">startModification</code> triggers of an entity.</p>\n<div class=\"note caution note_caution\" id=\"fas1665702598144__note_w1389ab1b7c11b7_w1390ab1b7c11_w1391ab1b7_w1392ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">CAUTION:</span> Never use the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">clear/e</span> statement in the\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">getFocus</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph\">startModification</code> triggers. This can\n            cause Uniface to enter an infinite loop.</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fas1665702598144__topic_d45952e1_d45953e1_d45954e1_d45955e1_d45956e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d884696e386\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fas1665702598144__p_d70076e1_d70077e1_d70078e1\">If the argument <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var> is omitted, all data in the component is cleared.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fas1665702598144__p_d70079e1_d70080e1_d70081e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">clear</span> statement clears all data from the component (by default) or, when the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/e</span> switch is given, from <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>. Data in the database is not affected by the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">clear</span> statement; any locked occurrences remain locked. The active path for the component is reset.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fas1665702598144__p_d70082e1_d70083e1_d70084e1\">One use for the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">clear</span> statement is when data has been added in a different component and the data displayed on the current form needs to be redisplayed.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fas1665702598144__topic_d45957e1_d45958e1_d45959e1_d45960e1_d45961e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d884696e419\">\n                       \n Component with Record behavior\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fas1665702598144__p_d70088e1_d70089e1_d70090e1\">Use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">clear/e</span> with care on a component with Record behavior. A Record component has only one outermost entity. If you have painted more than one outermost entity, when the Record component is compiled, Uniface expands the first outermost entity painted (that is, the upper, left-most) so that all other outermost entities become inner to the first. This means that using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">clear/e</span> to clear data from the first outmost entity on a Record component clears data from all the entities painted on the component.</p>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example clears the data entered when the user makes an entry that is not valid:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger leaveModified \n if ((salary &gt; 100000) &amp; (job != \"PRESIDENT\"))\n message \"Salary not valid\"\n clear/e \"entity\"\n endif\nend; leaveModified</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">In the example shown in following figure, component X calls Service Z to create a new occurrence of entity C:</p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"fas1665702598144__fig_w1384ab1b7c15b7b3_w1385ab1b7c15b7_w1386ab1b7c15_w1387ab1b7_w1388ab1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 1. </span>Using the clear statement to refresh updated data</figcaption>\n<img alt=\"Graphical content\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/usingclear.jpg?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"p\">The ProcScript for the Detail trigger is as follows:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger detail\n; save foreign key for occurrences displayed in entity C\n; set up foreign key, ready for retrieve\n; retrieve new data entered on service Z\n $1 = FOREIGN_KEY.C\n activate \"Z\".EXEC($1)\n clear/e \"C\"\n FOREIGN_KEY.C = $1\n retrieve/e \"C\"\nend</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tao1720020794963.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>erase</a><p>Activate the delete or deleteUp trigger for all occurrences in the component.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vxw1719821718668.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>release</a><p>Release database controls.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cyd1665702599286.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>retrieve</a><p>Activate the read trigger for the first outermost entity and all related entities, or for a specific entity.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7423320\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7423320\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "clear Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 23, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Clear data from the component or entity. clear{/e Entity} Copy Qualifiers Table 1. Qualifiers Qualifier Description /e Clears data from the specified entity, rather than the component. Parameters Table 2. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Entity String Entity to be cleared. Can be a string, or a field, variable, function, or parameter that evaluates to a string containing the entity name. Return Values Table 3. Values returned in $status Value Meaning 0 Data was successfully cleared, or no entities are painted on the component. -3 Exceptional I/O error (hardware or software). -16 Network error: unknown. Table 4. Values commonly returned by $procerror following clear Value Error constant Meaning -2 through -12 <UIOSERR_*> Errors during database I/O. -16 through -30 <UNETERR_*> Errors during network I/O. -1102 <UPROCERR_ENTITY> The entity name provided is not a valid name or the entity is not painted on the component. Use Allowed in all component types. Not allowed in the getFocus and startModification triggers of an entity. CAUTION: Never use the clear/e statement in the getFocus or startModification triggers. This can cause Uniface to enter an infinite loop. Description If the argument Entity is omitted, all data in the component is cleared. The clear statement clears all data from the component (by default) or, when the /e switch is given, from Entity . Data in the database is not affected by the clear statement; any locked occurrences remain locked. The active path for the component is reset. One use for the clear statement is when data has been added in a different component and the data displayed on the current form needs to be redisplayed. Component with Record behavior Use clear/e with care on a component with Record behavior. A Record component has only one outermost entity. If you have painted more than one outermost entity, when the Record component is compiled, Uniface expands the first outermost entity painted (that is, the upper, left-most) so that all other outermost entities become inner to the first. This means that using clear/e to clear data from the first outmost entity on a Record component clears data from all the entities painted on the component. The following example clears the data entered when the user makes an entry that is not valid: trigger leaveModified if ((salary > 100000) & (job != \"PRESIDENT\")) message \"Salary not valid\" clear/e \"entity\" endif end; leaveModified Copy In the example shown in following figure, component X calls Service Z to create a new occurrence of entity C: Figure 1. Using the clear statement to refresh updated data The ProcScript for the Detail trigger is as follows: trigger detail ; save foreign key for occurrences displayed in entity C ; set up foreign key, ready for retrieve ; retrieve new data entered on service Z $1 = FOREIGN_KEY.C activate \"Z\".EXEC($1) clear/e \"C\" FOREIGN_KEY.C = $1 retrieve/e \"C\" end Copy Related Links erase Activate the delete or deleteUp trigger for all occurrences in the component. release Release database controls. retrieve Activate the read trigger for the first outermost entity and all related entities, or for a specific entity. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}